Package server.proxies

Class DepartureAirportProxy

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Thread
server.proxies.DepartureAirportProxy
All Implemented Interfaces:
HostessInterface, PassengerInterface, PilotInterface, java.lang.Runnable
public class DepartureAirportProxy
extends java.lang.Thread
implements PassengerInterface, HostessInterface, PilotInterface
Service provider agent for access to the Departure Airport. Implementation of a client-server model of type 2 (server replication). Communication is based on a communication channel under the TCP protocol.
